<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="congratulation-n">congratulation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kənˌgrætʃu'leɪʃn/    美 /kənˌgrætʃu'leɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[C] [常用复数]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>祝贺；庆贺：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’ve passed your driving test? Congratulations!
你通过驾照考试了？祝贺你！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I want to express my <strong>congratulations on</strong> your success.
我对你的成功表示祝贺。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— I got that job I wanted at the public library.
— <strong><em>_</em></strong> (祝贺你)! That’s good news.  （2014 陕西改）  </li>
<li>Please give my <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (祝贺) when you see her.   （2006 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. Congratulations  2. congratulations  </p></div>